        <h1>About the Ibhayi Pharmacy Prescription Management System</h1>
        <p>
            Welcome to the <strong>Ibhayi Pharmacy Prescription Management System</strong> – a secure, web-based application built specifically for Ibhayi Pharmacy, located in the Nelson Mandela Bay metro. This system is designed to streamline prescription management, medication dispensing, and stock control, enabling the pharmacy to operate efficiently while focusing on patient safety and regulatory compliance.
        </p>
        <p>
            Developed to replaces traditional manual processes with an integrated solution tailored for pharmacies that dispense prescription medications only. The system ensures accurate tracking of prescriptions, inventory, and staff activities, enhancing transparency and accountability.
        </p>

        <h2>Key System Features</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>User Roles & Authentication:</strong> Secure login for Pharmacy Managers, Pharmacists, and Customers with encrypted passwords and password recovery via email.</li>
            <li><strong>Pharmacy Management:</strong> Manage key details such as registration, contact information, responsible pharmacist, and supplier details.</li>
            <li><strong>Medication & Stock Management:</strong> Track medication details including schedule, dosage form, active ingredients, pricing, and reorder levels. Generate reports and manage stock levels and orders effectively.</li>
            <li><strong>Prescription Handling:</strong> Upload, store, and manage prescriptions in PDF format. Dispense medications with allergy alerts and track prescription repeats.</li>
            <li><strong>Customer Services:</strong> Register online, upload prescriptions, request dispensation, track repeat availability, and receive collection notifications via email.</li>
            <li><strong>Reporting:</strong> Generate customizable PDF reports grouped by patient, medication, doctor, schedule, or supplier for audits, stocktakes, or patient records.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>System Users & Responsibilities</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Pharmacy Manager:</strong> Oversee system configuration, manage stock, suppliers, doctors, pharmacists, and generate inventory reports and medication orders.</li>
            <li><strong>Pharmacist:</strong> Load and dispense prescriptions, manage patient safety alerts (e.g. allergies), and generate medication dispensing reports.</li>
            <li><strong>Customer:</strong> Register, upload and manage prescriptions, request medication to be prepared for collection, and track order history and repeats.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Our Vision</h2>
        <p>
            The Ibhayi Pharmacy Prescription Management System was developed to bring modern efficiency and reliability to prescription handling. By embracing digital workflows, our goal is to help Ibhayi Pharmacy deliver faster, safer, and more accurate service to its community. Through this system, we aim to support healthcare excellence and continuous operational improvement.
        </p>
